<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN">
<html>
<head>
<title>Help: Deleting an item</title>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
<link href="../style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>

<body>
<p class="titlebold">Deleting an item</p>
<p class="text">Open the site you want to edit and select Items. Click on the
[ X ] icon next to the item you want to delete. </p>
<p class="text"><strong>WARNING: Deleting an item is not undoable. All information related
  to that item (except for data related to an   order that has been placed with
  that item) will be lost.</strong></p>
</body>
</html>
